{"tid":1061371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台籍港區政協「台灣女孩」凌友詩以當中國人為榮  卻被爆有美國綠卡","createTime":"2019-03-14T10:57:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T13:27:36.000Z","uid":35790,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"9ca2478dd9df5dd313cc80dac7680f836577d4a3","tid":1061371,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:57:44.000Z","msg":"57歲「台灣女孩」凌友詩以當中國人為榮 卻被爆有綠卡...<br />\n<br />\n2019-03-14<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國全國政協委員凌友詩近日在北京舉行的政協會議上，以高八度音調、樣板式風格發表促統演說，成為兩岸關注焦點，背景也隨之曝光，凌友詩原來出身台灣，父親是前海軍副艦長，還被爆料手握美國綠卡，讓其促統言論受到不少嘲諷。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，凌友詩1962年生於台灣高雄，父親為前海軍副艦長，曾參與八二三砲戰。她16歲時舉家移居香港，於香港中文大學攻讀中文、政治與公共行政學碩士，接著再獲得香港大學政治哲學博士，之後進入政府部門工作。<br />\n<br />\n凌友詩在中國全國政協會議中發言自稱「我是一個在台灣出生，17歲移居到香港的台籍港區委員」、「今天，<span style=\"color: red;\">我站在人民大會堂的發言席，我要說，世界上只有1個中國，全中國的唯一合法代表政府，是中華人民共和國政府，我以能做為1個堂堂正正的中國人、參與國家的政治體制而自豪」。</span><br />\n<br />\n今天《聯合報》報導，立場「又紅又統」的凌友詩其實擁有美國綠卡。網友留言表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">「有綠卡的都特別愛國」</span>、「帶種放棄綠卡」、「真的很標準的中國印象人物」、「反美是工作，親美是生活」、「中共愛國標配：綠卡」。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"0a77a0508eee7e2f7675d1a52db48cead0c48e7a","tid":1061371,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T10:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd3634dca8be69cba58407815088fea61719716","tid":1061371,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:00:01.000Z","msg":"香港大把愛國人士都有外國居留權或國籍  有咩出奇！"},{"pid":"607b582ddf588472ec9c6e68da26660090118aa1","tid":1061371,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c201e3dcf1df7d5c5ed846a532ee8cb118d2224e","tid":1061371,"uid":26752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T11:33:17.000Z","msg":"57歲都仲女孩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7c3e86841fe73be59554cbfd943706ae8feeff","tid":1061371,"uid":51936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:12:06.000Z","msg":"睇咗新聞，忍唔住上黎講<br />\n為呢個女人有香港背景覺得可恥<br />\n果種奴才走狗嘴臉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"077493255de3da089f03d0b1ee7053417e276336","tid":1061371,"uid":28351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"57歲仲女孩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97bdbc8218f97487c904e1369ac7a1769c2c38d","tid":1061371,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"077493255de3da089f03d0b1ee7053417e276336","tid":1061371,"uid":28351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:14:45.000Z","msg":"57歲仲女孩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:38:14.000Z","msg":"啲記者都Onlun799<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618968c445868bbd78d0b30dcae262aeddce9145","tid":1061371,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T12:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac